  "1736830": {
    "name": "The Chewllers",
    "steam_appid": 1736830,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736830/extras/182bfc235024df781d7bc0208818cae5.poster.avif?t=1679690981\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736830/extras/182bfc235024df781d7bc0208818cae5.webm?t=1679690981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736830/extras/182bfc235024df781d7bc0208818cae5.mp4?t=1679690981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><i>Chewller Apocalypse in Virtual Reality!</i><br><br><strong>The Chewllers</strong> is a first-person shooter designed exclusively for virtual reality, where the player is immersed in a post-apocalyptic world full of post-apocalyptic Chewllers.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHEWLLERS</strong></h2>There are different types of Chewllers in the game. They are distinguished from each other by their funny behaviors and abilities. <br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Basic Chewller<br></li><li>Roller<br></li><li>Kamikaze<br></li><li>Flying<br></li><li>Shooter<br></li><li>Support<br></li><li>Thief<br></li><li>Dino Rider<br></li><li>Dragon<br></li><li>Beetle <br></li><li>Boss</li></ul><br>Each requires an individual approach. The harder it is to deal with monsters, the greater the chance of them dropping <strong>resources</strong>, <strong>items</strong>, and <strong>chests</strong>.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736830/extras/a4efa3612b47098e7c02ce16e18f05d9.poster.avif?t=1679690981\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736830/extras/a4efa3612b47098e7c02ce16e18f05d9.webm?t=1679690981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736830/extras/a4efa3612b47098e7c02ce16e18f05d9.mp4?t=1679690981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>WEAPONS</strong></h2><br>In the game, you will find <strong>primary </strong>and <strong>secondary </strong><strong>weapons</strong>. The main weapon that the player constantly has is <strong>upgrading </strong>up to <strong>5 Lvl</strong>. As for secondary weapons, there are <strong>6</strong> types of weapons that are functionally different from each other and have different roles All secondary weapons are upgraded up to <strong>3 Lvl</strong>. <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Sniper<br></li><li>Shotgun<br></li><li>Crossbow<br></li><li>Grenade launcher<br></li><li>Machine gun<br></li><li>Potato Catapult</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736830/extras/30ffd5248367852c2eb8572a2bc4ed8b.poster.avif?t=1679690981\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736830/extras/30ffd5248367852c2eb8572a2bc4ed8b.webm?t=1679690981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736830/extras/30ffd5248367852c2eb8572a2bc4ed8b.mp4?t=1679690981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>THROWABLE ITEMS</strong></h2>There are <strong>7</strong> types of <strong>items </strong>available from which the player can make a bunch of weird and practical <strong>combinations </strong>of throwables. Creativity is the limit. Each of them has its own significance and uniqueness in various cases.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Pumpkin<br></li><li>Paint spray<br></li><li>Grenade<br></li><li>Fuel tank<br></li><li>Sensor<br></li><li>Perfume<br></li><li>Poison flask</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736830/extras/c6ccf6a6a5631e2bcec6b4df8ee11465.poster.avif?t=1679690981\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736830/extras/c6ccf6a6a5631e2bcec6b4df8ee11465.webm?t=1679690981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736830/extras/c6ccf6a6a5631e2bcec6b4df8ee11465.mp4?t=1679690981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GAME MODES</strong></h2><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>SinglePlayer Campaign</strong></li></ul>Game built from all existing locations of virtual reality, which creates a lot of <strong>challenges</strong>, where you can complete additional <strong>tasks</strong>, receive new <strong>rewards </strong>and improve <strong>progress</strong>.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>MultiPlayer Campaign</strong></li></ul>Play with <strong>friends</strong>, Join forces in the <strong>co-op mode</strong>, create your own unique <strong>strategies</strong>, overcome new location challenges and become the <strong>Chewller Slayer</strong>! But keep in mind: the more chewing items the base consists of, the more exciting the Chewllers are.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736830/extras/4680f3bd8b53873285f0fe23cd247b07.poster.avif?t=1679690981\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736830/extras/4680f3bd8b53873285f0fe23cd247b07.webm?t=1679690981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1736830/extras/4680f3bd8b53873285f0fe23cd247b07.mp4?t=1679690981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>",
